@rrpawar96  Besides changes suggested by @vorburger , I want you to address the previously discussed points : remove extra white spaces and lines.  Once this is done make sure you run the test cases and manually verify normal savings and loan application functionalities ( by installing Community App).  If regression is fine, I would give a go ahead from me to merge this PR. 

Having said that, as a Phase two( or in this phase itself- if required by other members) We have to add API documentation of this feature.

Once this is done, I would request you to take up Front end support for this feature. Any further bug fixes and enhancements can be addressed during this phase.

We are splitting this work in phases just to avoid the hassles of rebasing the code from time to time.

@vorburger @awasum  let me know what you guys think about this.

